org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.talon

Class TalonParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.talon.TalonParameters

  • public abstract class TalonParameters
extends Object
    Configure Talon SRX parameters. This class will read CANTalon configurations located in TOML configuration objects registered using the register(UnmodifiableConfig) class method.

    Multiple configurations can be registered by calling the register method repeatedly.

    See Also:
    CANTalon

        public static void register(com.electronwill.nightconfig.core.UnmodifiableConfig talonConfigs)
        Register a new configuration file containing Talon parameters. These parameter objects will be merged with existing parameter objects. If a new parameter object has the same name as an existing object, the old object will be overwritten.
        Parameters:
